00:04:24.079 --> 00:04:25.839
Exactement 104.

00:04:25.839 --> 00:04:26.879
Très bien. Ensuite,

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:28.279
Su Beilu.

00:04:28.279 --> 00:04:29.199
À ton tour,

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:30.000
Su Beilu.

